-NADJA: Bloody hell.

09:46.253 --> 09:48.455
(shouts in foreign language)

09:48.488 --> 09:50.590
-That looks like me.
-What have you done?

09:50.624 --> 09:52.159
Get off me.

09:52.192 --> 09:55.062
(ghosts speaking
foreign languages)

09:55.095 --> 09:56.496
LASZLO:
Be quiet.

09:59.132 --> 10:01.669
Laszlo, he's wearing
your old night skirt.

10:01.702 --> 10:04.604
