by the looks of it.

10:06.339 --> 10:08.776
It's like looking in the mirror.

10:08.809 --> 10:11.144
So handsome.

10:11.178 --> 10:12.646
I didn't even know

10:12.680 --> 10:15.448
I had any unfinished business
when I died.

10:15.482 --> 10:16.784
But, as you can see,

10:16.817 --> 10:18.318
I have a ghost,

10:18.351 --> 10:19.586
so there must be something.

10:19.619 --> 10:21.421
(ghost shouting
in foreign language)

10:21.454 --> 10:23.891
Guillermo, can you help him
with that, please?

10:25.893 --> 10:29.362
-He seems very agitated
and restless.
-(shouting)

10:29.396 --> 10:33.834
And also, he doesn't seem
to speak any English.

10:33.867 --> 10:35.035
Excuse me.

10:35.068 --> 10:39.472
(speaking foreign language)

10:39.506 --> 10:41.641
I can't believe
I've completely forgotten

10:41.675 --> 10:43.276
how to speak
Al Qolnidarese.

10:43.310 --> 10:46.146
My own language.
So embarrassing.

10:46.179 --> 10:48.115
Guillermo, what is he saying?

10:48.148 --> 10:50.150
How-how would I know?

10:50.183 --> 10:53.320
I do remember how to say
"Good morning," though.

10:53.353 --> 10:54.788
GHOST NANDOR:
Aspam...

10:54.822 --> 10:56.757
Sob bekher.

10:57.825 --> 10:59.026
Baleh?

10:59.059 --> 11:00.861
Sob bekher.

